{"tid":632356,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"被店員指控非法入侵... 黑人去Starbucks借廁所遭逮捕","createTime":"2018-04-17T10:03:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-18T00:35:23.000Z","uid":66943,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"46a1492f80f9a3be40c85f77a9ee84a183bb5ed7","tid":632356,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T10:03:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpzLbTKv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpzLbTKv.jpg&h=84696698&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">美國費城有黑人到星巴克借廁所，竟被店員報警逮捕。（圖擷自Melissa DePino推特）</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://video.twimg.com/ext_tw_video/984539534871408640/pu/pl/720x1280/rMy628VMfgjGdwkM.m3u8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvideo.twimg.com%2Fext_tw_video%2F984539534871408640%2Fpu%2Fpl%2F720x1280%2FrMy628VMfgjGdwkM.m3u8&d=nwxsaOv4DVDwxxgDlY5mHWxr1Wzy5cvmMlqj7aCMUDs%3D&h=91ea2a39\" target=\"_blank\">https://video.twimg.com/ext_tw_video/984539534871408640/pu/pl/720x1280/rMy628VMfgjGdwkM.m3u8</a><br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕美國種族歧視問題又引起爭議！費城2名黑人到Starbucks沒有消費想借廁所，店員要求他們離開遭到拒絕後，竟直接報警指控「非法入侵」，導致黑人雙雙被趕來的警察逮捕，不少美國網友得知消息後義憤填膺，直說2人遭到不平等待遇。<br />\n<br />\n據《ABC》報導，該事件發生在12日，店內顧客德皮諾（Melissa DePino）拍攝下逮捕過程，她透露星巴克員工朝2名黑人大聲喊叫，要他們消費或者是直接離開。星巴克人員還說，若是不付錢就別想借廁所，黑人則靜靜地沒有回應。<br />\n<br />\n過了不久幾名單車巡警前來將2名黑人逮捕，此時有白人顧客挺身而出，強調他們沒有做錯事，為何要被帶走？警方事後則表示，現場員警只是做了應該做的事，連續3次詢問黑人是否可以離開Starbucks，因為他們被指控非法入侵，不過遭到黑人拒絕，於是警察只好按照SOP將黑人上銬。<br />\n<br />\n星巴克公司在事情發酵後對此道歉，強調不會對2名黑人提出指控，費城地區檢察官也拒絕處理此案，費城市長肯尼（Jim Kenney）則說，他看到影片後心都碎了，將會聯繫Starbucks討論此事，並對警察SOP展開徹底的檢討。"},{"pid":"31d8aafe3be89c6270307545f3462abea3e02d9d","tid":632356,"uid":6327,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T10:07:57.000Z","msg":"黑人應該拉曬入去坐監就岩"},{"pid":"da79a3018dd41a031a6d32aa7d1ba5844f77fe0d","tid":632356,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T17:04:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"041c90270e211eaa43d157f6068cd873f6c31688","tid":632356,"uid":22553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T00:17:08.000Z","msg":"一定又係歧視啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9cdaeea8da90a512e9e8fcba4121861185cc9c4","tid":632356,"uid":85586,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"041c90270e211eaa43d157f6068cd873f6c31688","tid":632356,"uid":22553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T00:17:08.000Z","msg":"一定又係歧視啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T00:26:52.000Z","msg":"黑人依家真係好屈<br />\n咩事都可以用種族歧視擋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"008913581031b56870877dea34b35b6111ca00a5","tid":632356,"uid":22553,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c9cdaeea8da90a512e9e8fcba4121861185cc9c4","tid":632356,"uid":85586,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"041c90270e211eaa43d157f6068cd873f6c31688","tid":632356,"uid":22553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T00:17:08.000Z","msg":"一定又係歧視啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T00:26:52.000Z","msg":"黑人依家真係好屈<br />\n咩事都可以用種族歧視擋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T00:35:23.000Z","msg":"同蝗一樣"}]}